# Turbopack ignore - skip watching these files for faster HMR
**/node_modules/**
**/.next/**
**/.git/**
**/dist/**
**/build/**
**/coverage/**
**/*.test.ts
**/*.test.tsx
**/*.spec.ts
**/*.spec.tsx
**/test-results/**
**/playwright-report/**
**/.vscode/**
**/.claude/**
**/docs/**
**/*.md
**/scripts/seed-*.ts
